Description: Swedish Union Catalogue. Swedish National Bibliography and authority data. The National Bibliography and authority data is part of Libris- the Swedish Union Catalogue- and the long term goal is to release the whole database under an open license. The data contains links to Wikipedia- DBPedia- LC Authorities (names and subjects) and VIAF.
